@node OtherToRGB "OtherToRGB"

OTHERTORGB (2.0)

   @{b}FORMAT@{ub}
      OtherToRGB Mode/N/A,V1/N/A,V2/N/A,V3/N/A,V4/N
      Other2RGB Mode/N/A,V1/N/A,V2/N/A,V3/N/A,V4/N

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
      Convert from a foreign colorspace back to RGB.

   @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
      @{u}Mode@{uu}
	 Colorspace to convert from:

	 0 = RGB	(3 args)
	    1 = HSV	   (3 args)
	    2 = CMY	   (3 args)
	    3 = CMYK	   (4 args)
	    4 = YIQ	   (3 args)
	    5 = YUV	   (3 args)

      @{u}V1,V2,V3,V4@{uu}
	 The values of the color components that are being converted.

   @{b}RESULT@{ub}
      Returns the converted color in RESULT in the form:

	 <red:0-255> <green:0-255> <blue:0-255>
   @{b}SEE ALSO@{ub}
      RGBToOther

@endnode

