@node SortPalette "SortPalette"

SORTPALETTE

   @{b}FORMAT@{ub}
      SortPalette Up/S,Down/S

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
      Sort the colors in the active range of current palette.

   @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
      @{u}Up,Down@{uu}
	 Direction in which to sort the colors.  Up is in order of
	 increasing brightness, and Down is in order of decreasing
	 brightness.  If neight is specified, the standard sort order
	 choice requester is presented.  Only the colors in the active
	 range are affected.

