@node VirtualLine "VirtualLine"

VIRTUALLINE

   @{b}FORMAT@{ub}
      VirtualLine X1/N/A,Y1/N/A,X2/N/A,Y2/N/A

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
      Draw a line directly on the preview display.  This does not affect
      the current buffer.  The line is drawn in complement mode, so to
      erase it draw over the same location with another line.

   @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
      @{u}X1,Y1@{uu}
	 Starting coordinates of the line, in buffer pixels.

      @{u}X2,Y2@{uu}
	 Ending coordinates of the line, in buffer pixels.

