@node Zoom "Zoom"

ZOOM

   @{b}FORMAT@{ub}
      Zoom Direction/A,Mouse/S

   @{b}FUNCTION@{ub}
      Zoom the preview display into or out of the current buffer.

   @{b}INPUTS@{ub}
      @{u}Direction@{uu}
	 Direction of zoom; should be one of "In", "Out", or "Full" (to
	 zoom all the way back out to full screen).

      @{u}Mouse@{uu}
	 If specified, the zoom will be centered around the current mouse
	 coordinates.  Otherwise, it will be centered on the display.

   @{b}RESULT@{ub}
      None.

@endnode


